growth into your code.

00:19:58.610 --> 00:20:01.134
I guess you guys can
give me some ideas what

00:20:01.134 --> 00:20:01.800
that would like.

00:20:01.800 --> 00:20:05.390
How can you take out all
your frustrations on the code

00:20:05.390 --> 00:20:07.420
that you're doing?

00:20:07.420 --> 00:20:08.980
I'd love to hear that.

00:20:08.980 --> 00:20:11.370
But you do find in a whole
wide range of creative fields,

00:20:11.370 --> 00:20:13.820
a lot of people have
had these hardships,

00:20:13.820 --> 00:20:16.240
and creativity is
healing for them.

00:20:16.240 --> 00:20:17.305
There's art therapy.

00:20:17.305 --> 00:20:18.930
There's all these
emerging fields where

00:20:18.930 --> 00:20:20.764
creativity can be very healing.

00:20:20.764 --> 00:20:22.430
We talk about journaling
